(firstQuint)Clinical Evaluation of the Cochlear Nucleus CI532 Cochlear Implant in Adults.

 Appropriate candidates will receive a CI532 cochlear implant and be fit with the CP1000 sound processor.

 Imaging will be completed pre-op, intra-op, and post-op to assess implant location.

 Speech perception testing as well as subjective questionnaires will be administered over 12 months.

